(128, 1, '2017-10-26 07:00:05', '2017-10-26 07:00:05', 'RSV is a production house on the cutting edge of innovation, widely regarded as the go-to for creativity, and reliability. We pride ourselves on our ability to provide the paramount of quality service and devote the utmost attention to customer relationships. As such, we take special precaution to maintain the quality of our  screening process.\r\n\r\n<strong>Responsibilities:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Develop creative concepts and overall direction of projects</li>\r\n 	<li>Create briefs and proposals</li>\r\n 	<li>Manage and service accounts and client expectations</li>\r\n 	<li>Handle contract negotiations</li>\r\n 	<li>Monitor progress of projects and deliver final products by deadlines</li>\r\n 	<li>Source deals and network on behalf of RSV</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>R</strong><strong>equirements:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>1-2 years experience as an Account Manager or relevant role</li>\r\n 	<li>Some experience in video production workflow</li>\r\n 	<li>Goal orientated with a go-getter attitude</li>\r\n 	<li>Familiar with mac os, iworks, and adobe suite.</li>\r\n 	<li>Excellent communication skills; able to interact with and present to all levels of an organisation</li>\r\n 	<li>Ability to work silo and in a team setting</li>\r\n 	<li>Able to handle multiple projects at once</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBring relevant video production, marketing or campaign management portfolio if any.', 'Account Manager', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'account-manager', '', '', '2017-10-26 10:07:24', '2017-10-26 10:07:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/rsv/?post_type=career&#038;p=128', 0, 'career', '', 0),
